<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>لِمَ خَلَوْتَ؟<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٠٨ - حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَحَدَّثَنِي عَبْدُ الْمُؤْمِنِ الْمَوْصِلِيُّ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> قِيلَ لِرَاهِبٍ: بِمَا خَلَوْتَ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> بِطُولِ مُكْثِي<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>